Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations,\NSilverstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're officially the first\Nnon-Pegasus Wonderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!? That is such an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to thank\Nyou, Professor Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy. You're kicking\Noff our show.. right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So get up there\Nand make me proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait..! I don't have my uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream! Somehow, I\Nmissed a class all year
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the final\Nis today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't pass,\NI can't graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. That was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's even weirder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurp] Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, this isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Waaa! Make it stop!\NMake it stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You have all\Nanswered my summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You mean this\Nisn't my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends must be\Ndreaming together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,More like a\Nnightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? How\Ndo I pick just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They all look so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your version\Nof a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you bring us\Nhere, Headmare Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not Twilight. I am\Nmerely the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You all must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! I have\Nhorrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Is the Crystal\NEmpire under attack again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! We only have\Ntwenty highlighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're all orange!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How will everycreature\Ncolor code their notes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure you're the\Nonly one that does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still! Twenty isn't enough\Nfor the new school year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got plenty of\Ntime to order more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The friendship students\Nwon't be back until--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Uh...now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is\Na surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all\Nhere so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I send out the wrong\Nback-to-school date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're not\Nhere for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're back 'cause\Nthe Tree of Harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,called us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad it\Ndidn't reach out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We kinda have a special\Nconnection with it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,after last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Tree couldn't have\Ncalled you. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sombra destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe next time, ease in\Nwith those truth bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the\NElements of Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't that mean\Nthe Everfree Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will take over Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got that\Npart under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sombra won't\Nbe coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So...some good news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we see the tree ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...what's left of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you promise\Nto stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Castle of the\NTwo Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the safest place,\Nas you may remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not scared of\Npuckwudgies anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends save whole\Nschool from evil Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this happen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we hadn't gone\Nhome for summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we could've\Nsaved the Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I wish that Sombra\Nguy was still around,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so we could teach\Nhim a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That not bring back tree.\NOr Elements of Harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! We all saw and heard\Nthe Tree in our dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it talk to us\Nif it was really gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, if we close our eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and think really strong\Nfriendship thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree will get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. I've heard worse\Nsuggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[whispering]\NIs it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the Tree\Nreally IS gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we need to do\Nsomething to honor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good idea, Gallus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe that's why\Nthe tree called us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have used the last\Nof its magic to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd come here and\Nkeep its memory alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It did say it needed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Thorax (angry):{\i0}\N{\i1} Ocellus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are! The hive\Nhas been worried sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave\Nwithout telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time you and\Nyour friends did that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it almost brought\Nour kingdoms to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh sorry, Thorax. It\Nwas an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time, ask\Nbefore you run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now c'mon,\Nlet's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! She can't leave!\NWe have a...Dragon Quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's not a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This quest for {\i1}all{\i0} Yona\Nfriends. Need to help Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it might take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stay,\NHeadmare Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long you get\Npermission from your kingdoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that permission\Nslip in triplicate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or is one enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I like to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar: Hey, you're back! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I live locally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd do a\Nlittle cleaning up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a headstart, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar. Where's the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I got rid of it. To make\Nroom for our memorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. That's what you\Nguys were thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we remember the\NTree if it's totally gone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not gone! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted a new Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar. You know that's\Nnot the same tree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a symbol, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony heart in right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus: [growl]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This cave was supposed\Nto stay EXACTLY the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so future creatures could\Ncome visit and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the memory of the Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everycreature. I\Nthought I was helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Harmony\Nis a huge part
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of Equestrian history.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna honor it, we\Nneed to do better than THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like, with lots of artwork
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that represents the\Nsymbolism and deep emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it should be a museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the Tree's\Nhistory and artifacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a really big and\Nimposing monument,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so everycreature knows how\Npowerful the Tree was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we should turn\Nthis cave into a place
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for creatures to reflect\Non the Tree's true gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I like my idea better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more perfect\Nthan ANOTHER tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What would Headmare\NTwilight want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona! You've been awfully quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which idea do you like best?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona like when\Nfriends not argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe friends\Nlisten to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and make plan together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Nah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little guy.\NNeed a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Gallus: Step right up,{\i0}\N{\i1} walk this way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Welcome to the{\i0}\N{\i1} one, the only{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}magical Tree of\NHarmony museum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! See the\Nbirthplace of the Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Grown from the\Ntears of a basilisk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and tended day and\Nnight by Pony magicians,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,this is truly one of the\Nwonders of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Gallus? None of\Nthat actually true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Honoring the tree\Nmeans giving it a story
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that creatures will\Ncare about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It already HAS\Na great story!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but mine\Nmakes more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, can you\Njust keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My sapling doesn't\Nlike the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! It doesn't belong in\Nthe Tree's memorial anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,AND! If you think this is great,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:11:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,just wait until you see the\Nmystical Cave of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What dragon doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Making a memorial\Nstatue of the Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When creatures see this,\Nthey'll be super-impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Look like rock, not Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And honestly? I'm kinda\Nhaving a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,remembering what the\NTree looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm\Nalready forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Needs more "loyalty."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Yona!\NIt's not dry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What hippogriff\Npainting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Tree, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See? These are the emotions\Nits loss made me feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,dancing with the representations
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of elements of harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should label it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Brown isn't\Nan Element of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Yona! This fountain\Nis heavier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for creatures to\Nlook at as they honor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree's memory in quiet\Nthought and contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got some help and\Nguidance from the counselor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,at our Feelings Forum back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only positive energy\Nwill bloom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Gallus: WAIT! You{\i0}\N{\i1} can't go yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a whole puppet\Nshow of the time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree tested us\Nin the catacombs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,under the School of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't bring that hunk\Nof junk into my museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for your museum.\NIt's for my Tree memorial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So leave it OUTSIDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It BELONGS in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you DO!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My meditation garden is ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you have\Nbeen more careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This never\Nwould've happened
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if you all just\Nlistened to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And made the Tree some kind\Nof roadside attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmare Twilight is gonna\Nbe so mad when she sees
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,what you guys did to\Nthe Cave of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like some rainbow\Nart project was better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressionism!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad the Tree\Nisn't here to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all YOUR fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,AH QUIET!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends doing this\Nthe wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All remembering Tree of\NHarmony for what Tree WAS,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,not what Tree IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean "gone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Yona mean, even though\NTree not HERE here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tree here! In hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tree made friendship\Neven closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! We ran\Naway to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,right above this spot, the\NCastle of the Two Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And later on, the\NTree tested us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to show us we're\Nstronger as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It DID call us all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You mean the Tree of Harmony\Nlives on in our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I can't believe we\Njust got schooled by a yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks know things not forever.\NThat's why smash and rebuild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we took care\Nof the smashing part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe we should\Nstart building. Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't decided what\Nwe should do for the Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona have idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree! Where did\Nyou find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't\Nmove it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was kinda heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're just\Nmentioning this now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What important is that\NYona bring back branches
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so friends can rebuild!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebuild what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I know! Something\Nthat represents what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree is: the gateway\Nto our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What Ponies\Ncall it? Club... home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A treehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the tree\Nwould've liked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me lift this piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We celebrate our friendship ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We celebrate the Tree ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The memories inside us ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll build for all to see. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Tree brought us together ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Brought us together ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And even though it's gone ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Even though it's gone ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Our monument of friendship ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Can make the gift live on. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A piece from me,{\i0}\N{\i1} a piece from you. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll use the Tree,{\i0}\N{\i1} and we'll make do. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ If things don't fit,{\i0}\N{\i1} there's lots of glue. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Friends don't quit{\i0}\N{\i1} in the end ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ and together we'll{\i0}\N{\i1} see this through! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ It's hard to say farewell ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ To something you hold dear ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But goodbye isn't forever ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ As long as we are here. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The tree is in our memory ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Aaaahh! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Its roots have grown{\i0}\N{\i1} deep in our hearts ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Deep in our hearts...{\i0}\N{\i1} deep in our hearts ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Its branches{\i0}\N{\i1} raise our spirits ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Together we're all bound. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Forever it stands ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Lost but now it's found. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So lift a beam and{\i0}\N{\i1} build it strong. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Work as a team,{\i0}\N{\i1} It won't take long ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Hey Silverstream! I{\i0}\N{\i1} I think that's wrong. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We'll live the dream{\i0}\N{\i1} And sing our song! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And make the Tree ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Something all can see ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Is the place{\i0}\N{\i1} where we belong. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar: Well? What\Ndo you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uh ... kinda messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder: Yeah. Like a\Nbunch of different parts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all smooshed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw it's just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona think it perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everycreature, out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How.. did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[echoing] Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit of the Tree\Nhouse would have perished
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:19:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,without your selfless\Ndeeds and caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you seek\Nsolace, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friendship,\Nand the friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of future generations\Nwill always be safe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,within these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a burst of magic all\Nthe way over at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everycreature OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A little confused,\Nbut definitely OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Where did\Nthis come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We were kinda gonna\Nask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like part of\Nthe Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But how? I thought\Nit was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was. But when we\Nused the broken parts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to build something\Nnew, this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree has always\Nbeen good at surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When Starswirl planted\Nthe Tree's seed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't even know\Nwhat it would grow into!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the Tree\Nis still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,changing and adapting to be\Nwhatever Equestria needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A cool place\Nto hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me\Nthis is more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the Elements of\NHarmony may still be with us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's actually\Nreally reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did the Tree need OUR\Nhelp to become something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. If I had to guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say your friendship is\Nmore powerful than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yona know. Yona just\Nneed to remind friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who's going to\Ngive us the tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all\Ngo in.... together?
